        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer877961800" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14400587737539156852">Sometimes Mishima is better in small doses, and his short fiction achieves everything you need without the morbid drama. This collection includes the short story “Patriotism” which is a kind of lens through which much of Mishima’s life and work can be viewed. He even made a film version of this story, in a kind of art imitates life imitates art loop— a rehearsal for his final performance. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


