<span id="freeTextContainer55658252885752300">I enjoyed the series of short stories--granted I know little of the vast Japanese culture but each story had it&apos;s unique personality, giving small glimpses of the culture at large. Would recommend to others and definitely read again.</span>
  <span id="freeText55658252885752300" style="display:none">I enjoyed the series of short stories--granted I know little of the vast Japanese culture but each story had it's unique personality, giving small glimpses of the culture at large. Would recommend to others and definitely read again.</span>
