        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2353287186" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16743803812579856219">This is a collection of 10 short stories. All the stories are good. The stories, &apos;&apos;Patriotism&apos; and &apos;&apos;The Pearl&apos; stand out. Patriotism especially is exceptional, both regarding the content and the descriptive part. This story can also be dubbed as prophetic, since the author too committed seppuku in the end.<br/>Highly recommended for reading.</span>
  <span id="freeText16743803812579856219" style="display:none">This is a collection of 10 short stories. All the stories are good. The stories, ''Patriotism' and ''The Pearl' stand out. Patriotism especially is exceptional, both regarding the content and the descriptive part. This story can also be dubbed as prophetic, since the author too committed seppuku in the end.<br />Highly recommended for reading.</span>
